title: Jenkins and Jonez - The ‘These Boys Nice’ Era
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - The ‘These Boys Nice’ Era
description:
The guys discuss the era of basketball we’re in right now where it seems like there’s a 50-point game every night, where Kyrie Irving fits among the most skilled players ever, Tom Brady’s unretirement, what kinds of kids names are tenable or untenable, two of their favorite TV shows, and much more.
